@startuml
title Config Wiring

rectangle "Frontend (.env.local)" {
  note as N1
  VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
  end note
}

rectangle "Backend (main.py)" {
  note as N2
  CORSMiddleware:
    allow_origins=["http://localhost:5173"]
    allow_methods=["*"]
    allow_headers=["*"]
  end note
}

N1 -down-> N2 : HTTP calls resolve to API base\nCORS allows dev origin

@enduml
